name: vortex
description: vortices are used frequently as gateways for energies and spirits to travel from one plane to another, often identified by their distinct spiral form. closing them can be accomplished by a group of experienced mages, though very few can successfully open a vortex themselves. most of the time they emerge at their own volition. cast to invoke dynamism. inscribed by tenorless circa 2021 // elements collection [water]
